These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
Food: nectarine, peas, artichoke, garlic
Sport: handball, volleyball, cricket, badminton
Transport: airplane, boat, bus, ship
1. Transport:airplane == Food:garlic##1
2. Transport:bus is on the left of Sport:volleyball##1
3. Food:garlic is in an odd position##4
4. Transport:boat is on the left or right of Transport:ship##3
5. Sport:cricket is on the left or right of Food:nectarine##3
6. Transport:ship is on the left of Food:artichoke##1
7. Transport:boat is on the far left or far right##3
8. Transport:ship is between Sport:badminton and Food:nectarine##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Food         | garlic      | nectarine | peas | artichoke |
| Sport   | cricket | handball  | volleyball   | badminton    |
| Transport     | airplane     | bus    | ship    | boat      |

