.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
City: paris, miami, marseilles, venice
Nationality: american, japanese, mexican, polish
Game: snooker, monopoly, mah-jongg, chess
1. Game:monopoly is on the left or right of City:marseilles##3
2. City:venice == Nationality:mexican##1
3. City:marseilles is in an even position##4
4. Game:snooker is on the far right##1
5. Game:chess is on the far left##1
6. City:miami is on the left of Nationality:japanese##1
7. Nationality:american is between City:venice and City:miami##2
8. Nationality:polish is between Nationality:japanese and City:marseilles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| City         | venice | marseilles   | miami | paris  |
| Nationality   | mexican     | american | polish  | japanese |
| Game     | chess        | mah-jongg  | monopoly    | snooker |

