3. Game:scrabble == Cigar:cain##1
4. Game:scrabble is on the right of Cigar:montecristo##1
5. Cigar:montecristo is in an odd position##4
6. Nationality:canadian is between Cigar:prince and Nationality:american##2
7. Nationality:german is on the left of Game:billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Cigar          | alhambra | prince   | montecristo     | cain     |
| Nationality   | argentine  | german | canadian   | american  |
| Game     | bridge      | canasta | billiard | scrabble |

