1. Flower:daffodil is in an even position##4
2. Movie-Genre:disaster == Food:pineapple##1
3. Food:orange is on the right of Food:onion##1
4. Flower:dahlia is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:horror##3
5. Flower:daffodil == Food:onion##1
6. Movie-Genre:horror == Flower:marigold##1
7. Flower:rose == Movie-Genre:crime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | romance   | horror     | disaster |
| Flower   | rose  | daffodil      | marigold        | dahlia     |
